(deflayer nav_layer
  esc  f1   f2   f3   f4   f5   f6   f7   f8   f9   f10  f11  f12        ssrq slck pause
  grv  1    2    3    4    5    6    7    8    9    0    -    =    bspc  ins  home pgup        nlck kp/  kp*  kp-
  tab  home lmet @chw @wsp tab  ins  pgup ret  esc  p    RA-8 RA-9 ret   del  end  pgdn        kp7  kp8  kp9  kp+
  caps end  del  bspc @lsf pgdn left down up   rght ;    RA-' RA-0                             kp4  kp5  kp6
  lsft 102d z    c    @lct @wtb caps @lal @rct ,    .    /    rsft            up               kp1  kp2  kp3  kprt
  lctl lmet lalt           spc                 ralt rmet cmp  rctl       left down rght        kp0  kp.
